    %h1 VENUE
    %p The Red Dirt Ruby Conference will be held in downtown <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&source=s_q&hl=en&geocode=&q=Oklahoma+City,+OK&sll=35.478565,-97.163086&sspn=9.530509,16.062012&ie=UTF8&hq=&hnear=Oklahoma+City,+Oklahoma&ll=35.46756,-97.516428&spn=19.030195,32.124023&z=5">Oklahoma City, Oklahoma</a> at the <a href="http://www.coxconventioncenter.com/">Cox Convention Center</a>. The conference hotel will be the <a href="http://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/okcbr-renaissance-oklahoma-city-convention-center-hotel/">Renaissance Hotel</a>, located just adjacent to the convention center.

    .spacer.clear

    %h4 Convention Center
    %a{:href=>"http://www.coxconventioncenter.com/maps/images/popmap2.jpg"}
      %img{:src=>"http://www.coxconventioncenter.com/maps/images/popmap2.jpg",:class=>"right",:width=>125}
    %p The Red Dirt Ruby Conference has reserved rooms 17-21 on the second floor (Concourse Level) of the Cox Convention Center. Breakout rooms as well as seating in the area directly outside the meeting rooms will be available for discussions, ad hoc presentations, work or other activities. An expo area for sponsor and vendor booths we be available. Wifi internet access will be provided throughout the area. Access to the conference hotel is conveniently provided by a skywalk on the second level.  
    
    .clear
    
